# SQLite MCP Server Settings
# Use this file to configure the SQLite MCP server for Claude Desktop
#
# Format:
# SETTING_NAME=value
#
# Optional Settings:
# -----------------
# DOCKER_IMAGE - Docker image name and tag (default: mcp/sqlite:latest)
# RESTART_CLAUDE - Whether to restart Claude Desktop if it's running (true/false, default: true)
# DATABASE_PATH - Path to SQLite database file (default: ./sqlite.db)
#
# Examples:
# DOCKER_IMAGE=mcp/sqlite:custom
# RESTART_CLAUDE=false
# DATABASE_PATH=/path/to/database.db
#
# Default settings (uncomment and modify as needed):
# DOCKER_IMAGE=mcp/sqlite:latest
# RESTART_CLAUDE=true
# DATABASE_PATH=./sqlite.db
